**Ambitious workflows:** As models get more capable, your deacon patrol loops could include autonomous pre-flight validation that detects and repairs Dolt corruption before patrol logic begins — turning fragile routines into self-healing workflows. Your mayor→deacon handoffs could evolve into parallel agent spawning with machine-readable state contracts, so multiple agents work simultaneously on patrol, triage, and infrastructure without losing context between sessions. See _On the Horizon_.

